cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV. 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving neural machine translation systems. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as NMT is a subfield of AI. The use of gates and pretraining also suggests it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of NMT could also suggest it belongs to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as NMT is used in image captioning and other computer vision tasks.
